        <li>No legal issues tolerated</li>
        <li>Business track record: 3+ years</li>
        <li>Collateral often required</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Common Rejection Reasons</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Late payments: 2+ times</li>
        <li>Credit card defaults</li>
        <li>Previous loan rejections</li>
